<p style="color:Orange;font-size:1.8vw;text-align: center;line-height:2">

Rules of play
<li style="color:SeaGreen;font-size:1vw;line-height:1.7">    Everyone starts from the soccerball with the hole number.</li>
<li style="color:SeaGreen;font-size:1vw;line-height:1.7">    On the holes where this is applicable, the ball needs to be player through the gate and/or obstacle, before being kicked in the hole.</li>
<li style="color:SeaGreen;font-size:1vw;line-height:1.7">    Count the amount of attempts to get the ball in the hole.</li>
<li style="color:SeaGreen;font-size:1vw;line-height:1.7">    If the ball goes outside the fence or in the bushes/flowers, you pick up the ball and place it back on the course. You also get 1 penalty point.</li>
<br>

</p>

